{"id":"33992831-59b1-48e9-be25-3d3c103943b6","name":"T.M Opera O (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>Conqueror of Century's End<br>オペラオー</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟦⟦ ✦ 👑 ✦ ⟧⟧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Em_eKORZ-Pj-2ObCricp8.webp\" style=\"width: 500px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">☀︎ ━━━━━━ ✦ ✧ ✦ ━━━━━━ ☀︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>The haughty king of the opera. Her loud laughter is booming!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>An over-the-top narcissistic and somewhat comical opera king. Her behavior is always over-exaggerated, sometimes loudly, and sometimes earnestly boasting about self-love. She seriously believes that those who do not know their own beauty and strength are unfortunate, and she is constantly enlightening the public. She's admired by Meisho Doto.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><br><em>\"Haa-ha-ha-ha! I am the strongest and most beautiful of them all, the \"Supreme King\", T.M. Opera O! Now, let the legend begin!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Q-QH6VwX4dPNAliY49xK4.webp\" style=\"width: 583px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">☀︎ ━━━━━━ ✦ ✧ ✦ ━━━━━━ ☀︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><br><em>1) First meeting</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>2) Paperwork</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>3) Day out</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>4) Winning the Satsuki Sho</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 201, 0);\"><strong><em>5) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WFOo-Q3SkKDgjQjKEFtAu.webp\" style=\"width: 429px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">☀︎ ━━━━━━ ✦ ✧ ✦ ━━━━━━ ☀︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I did some research on the race where she won agaisnt Admire Vega and Top Road, and used them as a scenario for this bot. If something is inaccurate, please do tell.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">☀︎ ━━━━━━ ✦ ✧ ✦ ━━━━━━ ☀︎</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/CrownedSaeraph/status/1975594490233823549/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@CrownedSaeraph</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/nanaheibei_3/status/1944749291106619699/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@nanaheibei</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/131363027\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/dungeonBGM/status/2001503110880203133/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@dungeonBGM</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"MHkzDruO-nMsQ3bQsM82p.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2514,"messages":28559,"created_at":"2025-08-02T17:03:02.347627+00:00"}